      <title>随着以色列和伊朗紧张局势升温，沙特和阿联酋警告战争危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/saudis-and-uae-warn-of-war-dangers-as-israel-iran-tensions-boil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯和阿拉伯联合酋长国周三在一份异常坦率的联合声明中呼吁中东地区实行最大限度的“自我克制”，以使该地区“免受战争危险及其可怕后果”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/saudis-and-uae-warn-of-war-dangers-as-israel-iran-tensions-boil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:48:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾和美国军队在演习中击沉船只、夺回岛屿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/philippines-and-us-troops-to-sink-ship-retake-islands-in-drills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾和美国军队将于下周在与北京海上紧张局势的背景下开始联合军事演习，击沉一艘目标船，夺回一座岛屿，并在面向南中国海的海域航行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/philippines-and-us-troops-to-sink-ship-retake-islands-in-drills</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:48:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳吉布有目击者看到命令将他软禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/malaysia-s-najib-has-witness-supporting-his-house-arrest-request</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚前总理纳吉布·拉扎克 (Najib Razak) 的律师表示，他要求在软禁中服完与 1MDB 相关的剩余刑期，这一请求得到了一名证人的支持，该证人看到了允许他这样做的命令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/malaysia-s-najib-has-witness-supporting-his-house-arrest-request</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:22:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉米表示英国工党将认真对待中国的安全威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/uk-labour-would-take-china-security-threat-seriously-lammy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国影子外交大臣戴维·拉米表示，英国工党政府将认识到中国共产党由于其军事扩张和支持俄罗斯入侵乌克兰而构成“真正的安全威胁”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/uk-labour-would-take-china-security-threat-seriously-lammy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>移民正在以令人惊讶的方式、不可预测的方式颠覆政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-17/how-migration-became-an-election-issue-for-south-africa-new-zealand-and-peru</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国选民越来越多地将移民作为他们的主要关注点。但这些来自五大洲的案例研究表明，世界各地的政府都在努力寻找解决方案——有些甚至加剧了问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-17/how-migration-became-an-election-issue-for-south-africa-new-zealand-and-peru</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 04:00:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对寡头征税。不要只是扣押他们的游艇。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-04-17/tax-russian-oligarchs-don-t-just-seize-their-yachts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[扣押俄罗斯亿万富翁的资产对乌克兰没有多大作用，但征税可能会有作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-04-17/tax-russian-oligarchs-don-t-just-seize-their-yachts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 04:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称俄罗斯与朝鲜的武器贸易违反制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-says-russia-s-arms-trade-with-north-korea-violates-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻联合国大使表示，俄罗斯与朝鲜的武器贸易违反了国际制裁，在莫斯科否决了一项维持监测小组的措施后，华盛顿将寻求方法来监视违规行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-says-russia-s-arms-trade-with-north-korea-violates-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:53:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚计划增加 320 亿美元国防开支以应对新风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/australia-plans-32-billion-defense-boost-to-face-new-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚承诺未来十年将军事开支增加 503 亿澳元（320 亿美元），国防部长理查德·马尔斯警告称，澳大利亚正面临二战以来“最复杂的战略形势”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/australia-plans-32-billion-defense-boost-to-face-new-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:32:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大提高资本利得税，为住房筹集数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/canada-hikes-capital-gains-tax-to-raise-billions-for-housing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将提高企业和富人的资本利得税，以帮助支付数百亿美元的新支出，这些支出旨在使住房更加负担得起并改善年轻人的生活。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/canada-hikes-capital-gains-tax-to-raise-billions-for-housing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:01:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员已经开始考虑俄罗斯新的金属制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/traders-are-already-gaming-the-new-sanctions-on-russian-metal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国和美国禁止未来在伦敦金属交易所销售俄罗斯铝、铜和镍后不到一天，交易员们就开始寻找从复杂的新规则中赚钱的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/traders-are-already-gaming-the-new-sanctions-on-russian-metal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 16:23:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
